I ever heard that name...

3
00:00:49,955 --> 00:00:52,561
Clouseau was just a little nobody.

4
00:00:52,725 --> 00:00:57,140
A police officer in some little village
far outside of Paris.

5
00:00:57,629 --> 00:01:01,236
He was the village idiot
as far as I could tell.

6
00:01:28,394 --> 00:01:30,374
Idiot, pull up.

7
