The case is closed.

25
00:02:43,969 --> 00:02:45,277
Needless to say...

26
00:02:45,437 --> 00:02:50,614
Clouseau did not qualify
for any advancement whatsoever.

27
00:02:50,776 --> 00:02:54,087
I never thought for a moment
I would have any use for him...

28
00:02:54,246 --> 00:02:56,920
until that fateful day.

29
00:02:58,116 --> 00:03:01,996
It was a perfect day for a murder.

30
00:03:02,154 --> 00:03:06,694
France against China, with the winner
advancing to the finals.

31
00:03:07,326 --> 00:03:11,968
I had been invited, as chief inspector
of the Police Nationale.

32
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:16,010
And because of my recent nomination
for the Medal of Honor.

33
00:03:16,168 --> 00:03:19,547
I have been nominated seven times.

34
00:03:20,005 --> 00:03:22,144
I have never won.

35
00:03:22,307 --> 00:03:26,619
But still, seven nominations...

36
00:03:26,778 --> 00:03:28,382
that's something.

37
00:03:28,747 --> 00:03:33,560
Anyway, the coach of
the French team, Yves Gluant...

38
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:37,223
came out for
his customary ovation.

39
00:03:39,591 --> 00:03:42,765
He raised his fist to the crowd.

40
00:03:42,928 --> 00:03:44,168
On it...

41
00:03:44,329 --> 00:03:46,331
The Pink Panther diamond.

42
00:03:51,637 --> 00:03:56,279
It was quite the symbol of pride
and victory for the French team.

43
00:03:57,242 --> 00:03:59,779
Gluant's girlfriend at that time...

44
00:03:59,945 --> 00:04:03,722
was Xania,
the international pop star.

45
00:04:03,882 --> 00:04:07,091
They had been having
quite a stormy affair.

46
00:04:34,913 --> 00:04:38,087
By the end of regulation time
the score was tied...

47
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:42,323
and the game
went into sudden death.

48
00:04:42,487 --> 00:04:45,764
For a patriotic Frenchman
and a true fan like myself...

49
00:04:45,924 --> 00:04:49,770
it was almost
too thrilling to believe.

50
00:04:50,495 --> 00:04:51,974
And then...

51
00:04:52,364 --> 00:04:54,537
the miracle.

52
00:05:09,481 --> 00:05:11,358
Yes! Yeah!

53
00:05:11,516 --> 00:05:14,326
Yes!

54
00:05:14,953 --> 00:05:16,523
Yes!

55
00:05:32,938 --> 00:05:35,316
Yes!

56
00:05:39,678 --> 00:05:44,559
And then, in front of a stadium
filled with people...

57
00:05:44,716 --> 00:05:47,356
Gluant collapsed...

58
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,930
dead.

59
00:05:49,888 --> 00:05:53,734
A poison dart in his neck.

60
00:05:53,892 --> 00:05:57,237
And the Pink Panther diamond...

61
00:05:59,031 --> 00:06:01,807
had disappeared.

62
00:09:11,957 --> 00:09:15,530
The newspapers fed on
Gluant's murder with a frenzy.

63
00:09:15,694 --> 00:09:18,197
For them, the world had stopped.

64
00:09:18,363 --> 00:09:19,603
For me...

65
00:09:20,131 --> 00:09:23,977
