for my greatest triumph.

66
00:09:26,438 --> 00:09:28,611
I know what we need
for the Gluant case.

67
00:09:29,407 --> 00:09:31,751
- What?
- An incompetent.

68
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:36,757
An unimaginative, by-the-book,
low-level incompetent...

69
00:09:36,915 --> 00:09:40,021
who will plod along,
getting nowhere...

70
00:09:40,185 --> 00:09:42,791
with the media
watching his every step.

71
00:09:42,954 --> 00:09:45,195
And while he is getting nowhere...

72
00:09:45,357 --> 00:09:48,463
I will put together the finest team
of investigators in France...

73
00:09:48,627 --> 00:09:51,870
and we will hunt down the killer,
retrieve the Pink Panther diamond...

74
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:55,273
and then the Medal of Honor
will be mine.

75
00:09:55,767 --> 00:09:58,111
And who is this incompetent?

76
00:09:58,503 --> 00:10:03,350
Oh, I think I know
the perfect man for the job.

77
00:10:03,708 --> 00:10:08,157
Find him and bring him to Paris.

78
00:10:08,613 --> 00:10:12,060
His name is Clouseau.

79
00:11:29,661 --> 00:11:31,106
Good morning, mademoiselle.

80
00:11:31,963 --> 00:11:34,409
I'll be right with you.

81
