- Could you help me down?
- Oh, yes, of course.

89
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:11,740
Oh, yes. Here, just... perhaps...

90
00:12:11,903 --> 00:12:13,814
- Yes, I...
- All right.

91
00:12:13,972 --> 00:12:16,179
- Wait.
- Yeah.

92
00:12:16,341 --> 00:12:19,550
Don't jump. Yes, that's good.
All right.

93
00:12:19,711 --> 00:12:23,022
I think if you put
your leg right there...

94
00:12:23,181 --> 00:12:25,923
- Okay.
- Yes. Okay.

95
00:12:27,385 --> 00:12:28,955
Yes.

96
00:12:30,555 --> 00:12:32,933
- I can't see anything.
- Maybe over here?

97
00:12:33,091 --> 00:12:35,196
- Yes, okay.
- Okay.

98
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,397
Over here.

99
00:12:42,801 --> 00:12:44,872
The inspector will see you now.

100
00:12:45,637 --> 00:12:47,913
He'll be right with you.

101
00:12:51,476 --> 00:12:52,784
Clouseau.

102
00:12:52,944 --> 00:12:55,220
- Clouseau.
- He's coming in.

103
00:12:56,381 --> 00:12:57,826
Good.

104
00:13:01,953 --> 00:13:05,162
Officer Jacques Clouseau,
gendarme, third class.

105
00:13:15,834 --> 00:13:20,146
- That had to hurt.
- No. No, not at all. No.

106
00:13:20,305 --> 00:13:22,546
Clouseau, the reason
we called you here...

107
00:13:23,341 --> 00:13:27,312
It is lovely weather we are having.

108
00:13:27,479 --> 00:13:32,724
I hope the weather continues.

109
00:13:39,491 --> 00:13:41,437
The area is secure.

110
00:13:41,593 --> 00:13:43,231
Oh, thank you.

111
00:13:43,394 --> 00:13:46,534
Clouseau, I have reviewed
your records, and it is clear to me...

112
00:13:46,698 --> 00:13:50,271
that a man of your talent
merits greater responsibility...

113
00:13:50,435 --> 00:13:52,244
than you have had
up to this point.

114
00:13:52,403 --> 00:13:55,714
I have decided to promote you
to inspector...

115
00:13:55,874 --> 00:13:59,378
the highest rank of any officer
in the republic.

116
00:13:59,544 --> 00:14:01,114
- Inspector?
- Exactly.

117
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:03,987
And your first case
is the Gluant murder...

118
00:14:04,149 --> 00:14:06,595
and theft of
the Pink Panther diamond.

119
00:14:06,751 --> 00:14:08,162
- I am honored.
