120
00:14:08,653 --> 00:14:11,190
Jacques Clouseau,
by the power vested in me...

121
00:14:11,356 --> 00:14:15,805
I hereby appoint you
full inspector...

122
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,906
with all of the...

123
