please.

124
00:14:29,207 --> 00:14:30,584
Oh, here, take my pen.

125
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:33,548
Thank you.

126
00:14:34,279 --> 00:14:39,627
One does not often see
the traditional French fountain pen.

127
00:14:44,255 --> 00:14:47,065
I will cherish this forever.

128
00:14:47,392 --> 00:14:49,963
No. It is not a gift.

129
00:14:50,128 --> 00:14:53,007
That was given to me
by the mayor of Paris.

130
00:14:53,731 --> 00:14:55,176
Well, then...

131
00:14:55,333 --> 00:14:56,778
I cannot accept this.

132
00:14:59,470 --> 00:15:00,972
The press conference.

133
00:15:01,973 --> 00:15:04,817
Yes. Clouseau, there is
a press conference...

134
00:15:04,976 --> 00:15:07,923
in just a few minutes
down the hall...

135
00:15:08,079 --> 00:15:09,786
to introduce you to the media.

136
00:15:09,948 --> 00:15:12,224
We'll meet you there.
And, Clouseau?

137
00:15:12,383 --> 00:15:13,828
Yes?

138
00:15:14,586 --> 00:15:15,826
Good luck.

139
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:18,100
Good luck to you.

140
00:15:18,256 --> 00:15:20,759
