141
00:15:21,192 --> 00:15:22,762
Go under the arch...

142
00:15:22,927 --> 00:15:25,703
through the door on the right
and down the hall.

143
00:15:28,666 --> 00:15:30,145
Well...

144
00:15:34,939 --> 00:15:37,681
The area is still secure.

145
00:15:39,077 --> 00:15:40,784
Thank you.

146
00:15:44,082 --> 00:15:45,789
He's perfect.

