That Gluant did not
want to be killed.

156
00:16:16,547 --> 00:16:19,756
Everything else follows
like liquid mercury...

157
00:16:19,917 --> 00:16:22,761
flowing down a... a...

158
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:25,992
